## **B. Gambaran Umum** 

Program Studi S1 Sains Data FMIPA Universitas Negeri Surabaya memiliki visi _“to become a provider of education, research and application of science and technology in the field of data science based on edu-technoecopreneurship and with a global reputation.”_ Dalam rangka mewujudkan visi tersebut, prodi menyelenggarakan pendidikan, penelitian, dan pengabdian masyarakat yang adaptif, inovatif, serta berbasis edu-technoecopreneurship.
